  • Throw on a cute hoodie the next time you're feeling cold

    Step out in style with this cute Unisex Hoodie! It's the perfect way to show off your kawaii flair featuring Boba the Brown Bear illustrated on the front. Plus, you get to choose between five pastel colors and four sizes, so you can get a snug fit that will keep you cosy and lookin' cute all day long!

    Measurements are shown below. We recommend comparing the measurements to a hoodie that fits to avoid any disappointment. If in doubt, just go one size up because a larger hoodie is always comfy to wear!
